_______________________________________________________________________________
"Psychic Crush"            
        This is the randomized equivalent to psionic blast, for those
        who are feeling lucky.  It costs the same but whereas psionic
        blast does a flat amount damage, psychic crush does a random
        amount.  So the psionicist could get lucky and do extra damage
        for the same amount of sp.
 
SP Cost:  Variable	Guild Level:  6		Potential Points:  5
 
Command:  pcrush <object>
